These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different pets are kept: horse, cat, goldfish, rabbit, ferret, fish
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, aconite, orchid, begonia, amaryllis
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Pet   | fish | horse  | goldfish    | rabbit  | cat      | ferret    |
| Flower      | daffodil  | amaryllis | begonia | zinnia | orchid | aconite |

