.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, magic-tricks, woodworking, rock-climbing, collecting
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani, montecristo, tiparillo, chaman, oliveros
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | rock-climbing | reading | collecting | woodworking     | magic-tricks  |
| Cigar           | montecristo | bongani    | ritmeester      | oliveros  | tiparillo | chaman |

