.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, bellflower, tulip, aconite, lily
House: tower, modern, futuristic, craftsman, farmhouse, cape-cod
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growslily##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
6. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the modern house##1
7. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
8. the futuristic house is the person who growstulip##1
9. the person who growsbellflower is the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Flower   | tulip   | lily   | aconite      | marigold | zinnia  | bellflower   |
| House   | futuristic | cape-cod | tower | modern   | farmhouse | craftsman |

