.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, siglo, old-henry, blend, alhambra, dunhill
The people have 6 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, journalist, dancer, freelancer, fisherman
1. the mechanic is on the far left##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the freelancer is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the fisherman is the blend-smoker##1
6. the architect is on the right of the dancer##1
7. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the journalist is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | blend | cain      | siglo  | dunhill | alhambra |
| Job     | mechanic | fisherman  | freelancer | journalist | dancer  | architect    |

