.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, subway, airplane, boat, ship, taxi
There are 6 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia, purple, chestnut, ivory, black
 1. the person who likes purple is the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
10. the person driving the boat is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Transport         | boat | taxi | bike | ship | subway | airplane  |
| Color   | black  | chestnut  | purple  | pink | ivory      | fuchsia |

