.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, water, tea, cola, hot-chocolate
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, go, backgammon, snooker, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person playing snooker is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | water    | juice | cola     | soy-milk   | tea     |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble | poker | go | backgammon | mah-jongg |

