6. the person who likes orange is the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
