3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the japanese##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the mexican is on the right of the japanese##1
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Nationality   | japanese | mexican  | colombian     | thai    | brazilian  | british          |
| Transport         | skateboard  | van | bus | scooter | boat | jet-ski |

