.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
There 6 different types of food: nectarine, eggplant, artichoke, pomegranate, mango, plum
6 different games are played: poker, go, snooker, canasta, scrabble, backgammon
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
7. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating plum##1
8. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
9. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Food    | mango | eggplant | pomegranate | plum    | nectarine | artichoke      |
| Game   | snooker   | poker     | go      | scrabble | backgammon           | canasta |

