4. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the train##1
8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Cigar          | old-henry | chaman   | davidoff  | pall-mall    | bongani  | fonseca |
| Transport   | ship   | train | van | airplane | roller | scooter |

