.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: techno, indie, ambient, hip-hop, blues, gospel
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, fantasy, documentary, satire, animation
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of blues##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
7. the fan of techno is the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of indie##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | techno     | ambient | indie | hip-hop | blues   |
| Movie-Genre        | animation | documentary | satire | fantasy   | superhero    | scientific |

