.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
City: hamburg, berlin, london, boston, prague, paris
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid, balloon-flower, amaryllis, azalea, bellflower
1. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
8. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| City   | prague | paris | boston    | berlin | london  | hamburg |
| Flower     | orchid    | azalea | amaryllis | bellflower   | balloon-flower | marigold    |

