4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the teacher##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the coach##1
7. the project-manager is the person watching animation movies##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
