.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, soy-milk, fanta, almond-milk, lemonade
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, february, october, july, may, august
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Beverage   | juice | lemonade     | almond-milk       | soy-milk  | fanta | mirinda    |
| Birthday     | august  | march | february | july | may  | october |

 